Phonegap/Cordova plugin for reading a plist file from NSBundle (iOS). 
This plugin right now solves only a single purpose of reading from plist file.

Future improvements will include,

1. Writing to plist file.
2. Reading any file from Bundle.
3. Open to receive suggestions related from the dev community.

Install:

The usual procedure to install phonegap/cordova plugin in an iOS env.

Usage:

Check the usage_sample.html and proj_plist_file_sample_with_key.plist files. the sample will showcase reading a key host_url from .plist file residing inside the project bundle.


